						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Rājarājakēśarivarman, who destroyed Sālai (Rājarāja I) Year 12: 997 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of seventy sheep by Uma Nīli Rājarāja-aṇukka Pallavaraiyan, to the god <hi rend="italic">(āḷvār)</hi> of the big temple <hi rend="italic">(peruntirukkōyil)</hi> at Marudāḍu in Marudāḍu-nāḍu in Veṇkunṟa-kkōṭṭam. </p>						

